        }

            cursor: pointer;

            border-radius: 8px;
            user-select: none;
        }

            background: #f3f4f8!important;
        }

        }

            font-size: 13px;
            width: 180px;
        }

            width: 20px;
            margin-right: 12px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

            font-size: 16px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .expander {
            margin-left: 6px;
            position: absolute;
            right: 12px;
            top: 18px;
            width: 7px;
            height: 12px;
        }
        .expander__expanded {
            width: 12px!important;
            height: 7px!important;
            top: 21px!important;
        }
        .item__selection {
            position: absolute;
            left: -13px;
            top: 14px;
            height: 12px;
            width: 3px;
            background: #0c94ff;
            display: none;
        }
        .item__selection__children {
            top: 7px;
            left: -43px;
        }
        .tree-item__selected .item__selection {
            display: block;
        }
        .footer {
            margin: 8px 0 8px 12px;
        }
        .footer__version {
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .footer__version-0,
        .footer__version-1 {
            color: #8991a9;
        }
        .footer__status-1 {
            color: #2562AA
        }
        .footer__status-2,
        .footer__status-3,
        .footer__version-2,
        .footer__version-3 {
            color: #C2140A;
        }
        .footer__status-3 {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer__version, .footer__status {

        }
    </style>
